snippet.title: Participant
snippet.description:
Participant ​​combines the power of a good story well told with real world impact and awareness around today’s most vital issues. As the leading media company dedicated to entertainment that inspires audiences to engage in positive social change, Participant has produced more than 100 feature and documentary films and episodic series that collectively have earned 82 Academy Award® nominations and 21 wins and have highlighted some of the most pressing issues of our time, including "Spotlight," "Contagion," "Lincoln," “Roma,” "American Factory," "Food, Inc.," “RBG,” "An Inconvenient Truth," “America to Me,” and “When They See Us.”
